---
By: Henry T. Hamblin
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 144
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Failure/Mistake
---
Though all men fail you, and all material sources fail, God is the same,
yesterday and today, and forever; and if you put your trust in God within,
you can never fail, because God, by nature, can never fail you.
